column5: Get a load of these fishing rapper's..lol~!      These underwater camera's are too cool I tell ya~!
haha, thats great.  Hes got a few good underwater camera vids there but ice ice fishing is too funny, thanks for sharing.
it's amazing that they resist such a lively minnow-guess that's why the old dead bait can be the trick
Pretty cool vids, Dam now that song is stuck in my head.

yes thats cool,its exactly what the lakers do where we fish in bancroft we can see them down the hole   cause the water is so clear it sure gets your heart pounding....    when they comein so fast and put the brakes on and you can see them down 20-25ft down i swear one day i will have a stroke...lol
You should see them on Simcoe. Logs I tell ya!
I will be singing that song for days.
Thanks Benthook,  You can learn a lot from those vids.  Very interesting
